descript.abstract: All existing and proposed parks in Montgomery County, sorted by existing/proposed and ownership
descript.purpose: Provide awareness of what land is parkland and under whose ownership. Identify areas that are proposed for acquisition through the master plan process

pubinfo.publish: Maryland-National Capital Park & Planning Commission (Montgomery County)
